<td style="text-align: right; font-size: 115%;">
<div class="noprint plainlinks hlist navbar mini" style="">
<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="/wiki/Template:Economic_systems_sidebar" title="Template:Economic systems sidebar"><span title="View this template" style="">v</span></a></li>
