<li id="cite_note-27"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-27">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book">Fernandes, Edesio; Varley, Ann (1998). <i>Illegal Cities: Law and Urban Change in Developing Countries</i>. London: Zed Books. pp.&#160;4.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Illegal+Cities%3A+Law+and+Urban+Change+in+Developing+Countries&amp;rft.aulast=Fernandes&amp;rft.aufirst=Edesio&amp;rft.au=Fernandes%2C%26%2332%3BEdesio&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B4&amp;rft.place=London&amp;rft.pub=Zed+Books&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Informal_sector"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-28"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-28">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book">Cities Alliance: Cities without Slums (2002). [http:// www.unchs.org/programmes/housingrights/expert_ group_ meeting.asp <i>Expert Group Meeting on Urban Indicators, Secure Tenure, Slums and Global Sample of Cities, Monday 28 to Wednesday 30 October 2002, .</i>]. Nairobi, Kenya: United Nations Human Settlements Programme (UN-HABITAT)<span class="printonly">. http:// www.unchs.org/programmes/housingrights/expert_ group_ meeting.asp</span>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Expert+Group+Meeting+on+Urban+Indicators%2C+Secure+Tenure%2C+Slums+and+Global+Sample+of+Cities%2C+Monday+28+to+Wednesday+30+October+2002%2C+.&amp;rft.aulast=Cities+Alliance%3A+Cities+without+Slums&amp;rft.au=Cities+Alliance%3A+Cities+without+Slums&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.place=Nairobi%2C+Kenya&amp;rft.pub=United+Nations+Human+Settlements+Programme+%28UN-HABITAT%29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2F+www.unchs.org%2Fprogrammes%2Fhousingrights%2Fexpert_+group_+meeting.asp&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Informal_sector"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
